msgstr ""

#. type: Table
#: _versions/2.13/guides/security-jwt.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Signature algorithm. Set it to `ES256` to support the Elliptic Curve signature algorithm."
msgstr "签名算法。将其设置为 `ES256` ，以支持椭圆曲线签名算法。"

#. type: Table
#: _versions/2.13/guides/security-jwt.adoc
